  "texts": [
    "The proposed NDT framework is further designed based on the above architecture.",
    "Each local domain has \"5 planes\" and a sub-domain digital twin entity.",
    "These planes are invoked to support the realization of digital twin functionalities.",
    "Moreover, the traditional control plane and user plane ensure communication between digital twin entities.",
    "The data plane provides data to the twin entities to update the twin models and ensure real-time interaction with the physical network."
  ],
